1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:38,539
[The Blooms at RUYI Pavilion]

3
00:01:38,630 --> 00:01:41,530
[Episode 8]

4
00:01:45,180 --> 00:01:46,330
It's a flower field.

5
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,200
Little follower.

6
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,210
Are you alright?

7
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,040
Wake up!

8
00:02:56,290 --> 00:02:57,829
[Mother!]

9
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:00,120
[Mother!]

10
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:03,990
[I'll return when you've solved the chess problem.]

11
00:03:11,730 --> 00:03:13,530
[I've solved the chess puzzle.]

12
00:03:13,620 --> 00:03:15,160
[I've solved the chess!]

13
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:17,230
[I've solved the chess puzzle.]

14
00:03:18,329 --> 00:03:19,650
[Your Highness.]

15
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,060
[Queen Dowager Wen has passed away.]

16
00:03:27,570 --> 00:03:29,329
[Mother.]

17
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:34,829
How are you feeling?

18
00:03:38,790 --> 00:03:39,760
I'm fine now.

19
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:42,750
You kept talking in sleep just now.

20
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:44,470
I dreamt of my mother.

21
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:49,310
I dreamt of the day my mother
was separated from me.

22
00:03:53,090 --> 00:03:54,590
You must be sad.

23
00:03:56,220 --> 00:03:57,710
Yes, so what?

24
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:00,880
Only at this time...

25
00:04:01,670 --> 00:04:03,120
that I can dream of her.

26
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,780
My mother's love for me...

27
00:04:06,820 --> 00:04:09,150
is my only motivation to live.

28
00:04:12,450 --> 00:04:13,330
Nong Nong.

29
00:04:14,170 --> 00:04:15,700
You still have things to do.

30
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,730
You leave first.

31
00:04:19,579 --> 00:04:20,550
Ms Fu.

32
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,880
I'll take care of him.

33
00:04:23,980 --> 00:04:24,860
Alright.

34
00:04:25,340 --> 00:04:26,660
If you need anything,

35
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:29,000
send someone to get me
at Ruyi Pavilion.

36
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:49,720
Rong'er.

37
00:04:49,810 --> 00:04:51,790
-Look at this.
-Let me see.

38
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:53,460
I wonder if she will like it.

39
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,610
-Take a look.
-Change another one.

40
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:59,750
Let's change to this.

41
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:01,860
It's not nice.

42
00:05:04,420 --> 00:05:05,820
-What about this?
-Miss.

43
00:05:06,530 --> 00:05:08,390
Someone asked me to bring it here.

44
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,280
My lady.

45
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:12,640
Did you order this?

46
00:05:12,730 --> 00:05:13,610
No.

47
00:05:13,790 --> 00:05:14,670
You ordered it?

48
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,380
-No.
-You?

49
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,260
Who asked you to bring it here?

50
00:05:20,260 --> 00:05:23,340
I'm not sure either.
Please enjoy your food.

51
00:05:23,420 --> 00:05:25,800
But it's not that refined
when look closely.

52
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,340
I'm not that satisfied.

53
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:43,490
[Cooling Cream]

54
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:47,140
[Cooling Cream]

55
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,430
[Ruyi Pavilion]

56
00:06:18,470 --> 00:06:21,680
[Guang Yang Palace]

57
00:06:22,650 --> 00:06:26,390
His Highness, Duke Su, is here!

58
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,700
Mother.

59
00:06:36,420 --> 00:06:38,659
Jin'er, why do you come suddenly?

60
00:06:39,980 --> 00:06:42,540
I came to visit you.

61
00:06:44,430 --> 00:06:46,140
Since you came that day,

62
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,820
I'm worried that...

63
00:06:48,210 --> 00:06:49,970
you're still mad at Hao'er.

64
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,270
He's still young.

65
00:06:54,110 --> 00:06:55,470
I won't get mad at him.

66
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,060
Don't worry.

67
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:03,700
How are you recently?

68
00:07:04,980 --> 00:07:05,860
I'm fine.

69
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,620
What about you?

70
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:10,960
I'm fine too.

71
00:07:14,610 --> 00:07:15,490
Consort Shu...

72
00:07:16,990 --> 00:07:18,180
Consort Shu, Duke Su.

73
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:20,840
Mr Dong brought people
from Ruyi Pavilion here.

74
00:07:20,900 --> 00:07:23,560
My brother brought someone
from Ruyi Pavilion?

75
00:07:24,860 --> 00:07:25,990
Since uncle is here,

76
00:07:26,490 --> 00:07:28,160
he must have something important.

77
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,400
I'll leave now.

78
00:07:31,990 --> 00:07:33,000
Alright.

79
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:38,200
Why do you come suddenly?

80
00:07:39,030 --> 00:07:41,090
Of course it's about your jewellery.

81
00:07:41,450 --> 00:07:42,510
Jewellery?

82
00:07:43,610 --> 00:07:46,010
Whoever started the trouble
should end it.

83
00:08:15,860 --> 00:08:17,390
This set of jewelleries...

84
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:20,000
is made by Ruyi Pavilion?

85
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:21,400
Yes,

86
00:08:21,490 --> 00:08:22,370
Consort Shu.

87
00:08:23,650 --> 00:08:26,240
The blooming flowers in spring
have their own style.

88
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:28,530
The dangling ornaments are like flowers
hanging on the head,

89
00:08:28,530 --> 00:08:30,380
and accompany by butterfly and dragonfly
silver hairpin.

90
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:31,780
It's hammered together.

91
00:08:32,539 --> 00:08:34,210
If you wear this Sunny Bright,

92
00:08:34,340 --> 00:08:36,500
it's like a flower that never wilts.

93
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:39,140
Sunny Bright?

94
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:40,630
Good.

95
00:08:44,810 --> 00:08:46,610
Why is there a floral fragrance?

96
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:48,860
It's a flower,
so it must have flower fragrance.

97
00:08:48,860 --> 00:08:50,180
With a special process,

98
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:52,290
we sealed the floral fragrance
in the silverware.

99
00:08:52,290 --> 00:08:54,490
The floral fragrance adds on the vitality.

100
00:08:54,490 --> 00:08:55,590
Not bad.

101
00:08:56,210 --> 00:08:57,350
I like it.

102
00:08:57,790 --> 00:08:59,600
Zhi Hui, give her a reward.

103
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:00,740
-Consort Shu.
-Yes.

104
00:09:00,740 --> 00:09:02,190
I dare not ask for a reward.

105
00:09:02,190 --> 00:09:05,010
My master, Liu Ru Yi,
didn't know about your taboo...

106
00:09:05,010 --> 00:09:06,270
and made a big mistake.

107
00:09:06,330 --> 00:09:09,100
Please forgive her.

108
00:09:09,580 --> 00:09:12,440
As a woman,
it's hard for her to endure in the prison.

109
00:09:13,060 --> 00:09:13,940
Wait a moment.

110
00:09:14,380 --> 00:09:16,320
What prison?

111
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:18,120
What do you mean?

112
00:09:21,020 --> 00:09:21,950
Your Highness.

113
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:24,500
I didn't say as I'm worried you'll be sad.

114
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,480
Ruyi Pavilion is presumptuous.

115
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:29,300
They sent head ornament with peony theme.

116
00:09:29,250 --> 00:09:31,670
[Zhi Hui, handmaiden of Consort Shu]

117
00:09:29,380 --> 00:09:31,580
I scolded them on behalf of you.

118
00:09:31,980 --> 00:09:32,860
Zhi Hui.

119
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,640
How could you act on your own?

120
00:09:34,930 --> 00:09:36,340
You dislike peony.

121
00:09:36,420 --> 00:09:38,490
Sometimes, you shed tears
when you see peony.

122
00:09:38,490 --> 00:09:41,260
If so, why should I send
this nasty thing...

123
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,580
to you?

124
00:09:43,380 --> 00:09:44,870
Just punish me if you want.

125
00:09:45,090 --> 00:09:47,160
I just don't want you to be sad.

126
00:09:47,690 --> 00:09:48,570
Forget it.

127
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:50,670
Go and reflect on yourself.

128
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:52,880
I'll cut your allowance for three months.

129
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,110
If you do it again,

130
00:09:54,380 --> 00:09:56,510
leave Guang Yang Palace immediately.

131
00:09:56,970 --> 00:09:58,380
Yes, Your Highness.

132
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:00,930
I felt weird...

133
00:10:01,060 --> 00:10:01,940
why would...

134
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,350
you come suddenly.

135
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:05,540
So this is what happened.

136
00:10:06,430 --> 00:10:07,630
Why didn't you ask me?

137
00:10:07,710 --> 00:10:08,590
This...

138
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:11,050
I don't want you to be sad.

139
00:10:11,540 --> 00:10:14,270
Ruyi Pavilion is jewellery store
for the people.

140
00:10:14,570 --> 00:10:16,680
Even if they have presented
a peony head ornament,

141
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:19,150
that's a miscommunication
between them and the palace.

142
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:22,010
As the saying goes,
one who doesn't know is not guilty.

143
00:10:22,010 --> 00:10:23,370
I won't blame them.

144
00:10:24,820 --> 00:10:28,610
It seems that you brought this jewellery
to make up for it.

145
00:10:29,490 --> 00:10:30,370
Yes.

146
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:35,030
I can see that you have put in
a lot of efforts.

147
00:10:36,310 --> 00:10:38,990
How did you get the idea
of this Sunny Bright?

148
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:41,100
To be honest,

149
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,640
when I was making jewelry,

150
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:44,100
I realized a truth.

151
00:10:45,330 --> 00:10:46,300
What truth?

152
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,480
Ruyi Pavilion
is a jewellery store.

153
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:51,310
To make a good jewelry,

154
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,940
it's hard to satisfy you,

155
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:55,290
but it's harder
to satisfy the people.

156
00:10:56,460 --> 00:10:57,780
Why do you say so?

157
00:10:59,190 --> 00:11:00,680
As a consort,

158
00:11:00,820 --> 00:11:02,680
if you want any kind of jewellery,

159
00:11:02,710 --> 00:11:04,780
every jewellery store in the world
will make it for you.

160
00:11:04,780 --> 00:11:06,310
You can offer a lot of money.

161
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,770
But for the people,

162
00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:09,570
they can't afford to pay...

163
00:11:09,660 --> 00:11:11,190
for a gold or silver thread.

164
00:11:11,380 --> 00:11:14,440
Your flower is made with gold and silver,
it won't wilt.

165
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:17,500
The people tie fresh flowers
and wear it on their head.

166
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,370
That's their Sunny Bright.

167
00:11:19,780 --> 00:11:21,640
It's easy to make the noble happy,

168
00:11:21,940 --> 00:11:23,870
but it's hard to make the people happy.

169
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:25,590
I hope in the future,
Ruyi Pavilion...

170
00:11:25,590 --> 00:11:27,130
can make the people happy.

171
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:30,120
If the people are happy,
you must be happy too.

172
00:11:30,430 --> 00:11:32,060
Make the people happy?

173
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,440
Alright.

174
00:11:35,710 --> 00:11:36,760
Well said.

175
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:40,810
Even if it's for the glory future
of Ruyi Pavilion,

176
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:43,450
I can't hold your master any longer.

177
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:46,580
Brother, let her go now.

178
00:11:47,810 --> 00:11:49,270
Thank you, Your Highness.

179
00:11:54,140 --> 00:11:55,020
How much?

180
00:11:55,070 --> 00:11:56,040
-Fifty taels.
-If you pass by,

181
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:57,140
-don't miss it!
-No counter-offer. It's 50 taels.

182
00:11:57,140 --> 00:11:58,500
-No, thanks.
-Take a look.

183
00:11:58,500 --> 00:11:59,470
-Mister.
-Mister.

184
00:11:59,470 --> 00:12:00,440
Take a look.

185
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:05,720
Stone signed by Farmer Ju Shui.

186
00:12:07,170 --> 00:12:08,880
How much is this stone?

187
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:12,350
This is a stone signed by
Farmer Ju Shui himself.

188
00:12:12,450 --> 00:12:13,330
Fifty taels.

189
00:12:14,250 --> 00:12:15,180
Forty taels.

190
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:16,940
If you get close and smell it,

191
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:20,320
it has the smell of Farmer Ju Shui.

192
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,380
Enough.

193
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:23,230
-Forget it.
-I'm not lying, mister.

194
00:12:23,230 --> 00:12:25,160
-It's really good.
-Fifty taels.

195
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:27,320
Take it.

196
00:12:35,020 --> 00:12:35,900
Young Master.

197
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:41,840
I've bought the stone as you ordered.

198
00:12:43,780 --> 00:12:45,620
They imitate the writing...

199
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:52,460
The matter in palace is settled too.

200
00:12:56,180 --> 00:12:58,210
Nong Nong and Ruyi Pavilion are safe.

201
00:12:58,210 --> 00:12:59,400
That makes me happy.

202
00:13:11,100 --> 00:13:11,980
Young Master.

203
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:14,400
The word "nong"...

204
00:13:15,980 --> 00:13:17,300
Is it wrong?

205
00:13:16,860 --> 00:13:18,540
[Farmer]

206
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:21,920
You didn't know...

207
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:24,210
but the name of Farmer Ju Shui...

208
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:26,340
was created because of Nong Nong.

209
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:29,450
I'm willing to care for Nong Nong,

210
00:13:30,020 --> 00:13:30,990
think of her...

211
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:32,970
and protect her.

212
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:37,700
I really didn't expect Consort Shu
to be so kind.

213
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:39,520
We can go pick up master tomorrow.

214
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:41,940
So, it has nothing to do
with Consort Duan?

215
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:42,960
That's right.

216
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:44,580
It has nothing to do
with Consort Shu.

217
00:13:44,580 --> 00:13:46,180
Not to mention Consort Duan.

218
00:13:46,340 --> 00:13:49,400
It's the handmaiden of Consort Shu
who acted on her own.

219
00:13:49,820 --> 00:13:50,790
But it's not her fault,

220
00:13:50,790 --> 00:13:52,330
she did it for Consort Shu.

221
00:13:52,590 --> 00:13:54,790
In short, it's all a misunderstanding.

222
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:59,100
So, it really has nothing to do with him.

223
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:02,180
What is it?

224
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,080
Nothing.

225
00:14:05,130 --> 00:14:06,010
Come.

226
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:08,360
I'll go with you tomorrow
to fetch Ms Liu.

227
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:10,100
Alright.

228
00:14:13,540 --> 00:14:21,240
[Imperial Storehouse]

229
00:14:18,730 --> 00:14:19,610
She's here.

230
00:14:20,530 --> 00:14:21,410
Master!

231
00:14:22,780 --> 00:14:23,660
Rong'er.

232
00:14:24,890 --> 00:14:25,900
Yuan.

233
00:14:25,990 --> 00:14:27,180
Ms Fu Xuan.

234
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:29,990
Thanks, Mr Dong.

235
00:14:32,150 --> 00:14:33,030
Rong'er.

236
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:35,450
Mr Dong told me everything
that you did.

237
00:14:35,670 --> 00:14:36,680
Thank you.

238
00:14:37,690 --> 00:14:38,620
And you two too.

239
00:14:38,970 --> 00:14:40,830
If not for your patient teaching,

240
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,810
also my sister and Yuan's help,

241
00:14:43,410 --> 00:14:46,490
I might not be able to make a jewellery
that satisfied Consort Shu.

242
00:14:46,490 --> 00:14:48,380
You two are close.

243
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:50,880
Be careful in everything from now on.

244
00:14:51,820 --> 00:14:53,550
I'll not forget your teaching.

245
00:14:53,930 --> 00:14:56,570
Thank you for your kindness, Mr Dong.

246
00:14:57,050 --> 00:14:58,900
You gave us a chance to make up for it.

247
00:14:58,900 --> 00:15:00,090
Instead of thanking me,

248
00:15:00,090 --> 00:15:01,890
it's better to thank Duke Su.

249
00:15:03,260 --> 00:15:04,180
Duke Su?

250
00:15:04,270 --> 00:15:05,150
Why?

251
00:15:05,410 --> 00:15:06,340
You didn't know?

252
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:09,060
If he didn't keep persuade me...

253
00:15:09,060 --> 00:15:10,380
to give you a chance,

254
00:15:10,740 --> 00:15:13,820
do you think this matter
can be resolved properly?

255
00:15:17,070 --> 00:15:18,000
Him?

256
00:15:19,890 --> 00:15:22,660
I'm so busy because of you recently.

257
00:15:22,790 --> 00:15:24,950
I can finally be at ease now.

258
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:26,690
Hurry up and go back.

259
00:15:27,280 --> 00:15:28,510
Thank you, Mr Dong.

260
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:40,540
Why are you standing here?
Let's go back.

261
00:15:41,620 --> 00:15:43,950
Cross over the brazier
and you'll be fine.

262
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,850
-This...
-Come.

263
00:15:46,950 --> 00:15:48,660
One, two, three.

264
00:15:53,150 --> 00:15:54,030
Master.

265
00:15:54,650 --> 00:15:56,380
You've suffered in the prison.

266
00:15:57,290 --> 00:15:59,350
I'll treat you well after you go back.

267
00:16:06,530 --> 00:16:07,410
Rong'er.

268
00:16:07,500 --> 00:16:08,380
Ms Liu.

269
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:10,710
You go back first, I've things to do.

270
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:12,160
What things?

271
00:16:18,100 --> 00:16:19,550
Master, let's go.

272
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:31,480
Little Marquis!

273
00:16:33,370 --> 00:16:34,300
Little Marquis.

274
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:37,550
Ms Fu.

275
00:16:38,210 --> 00:16:40,100
What advice do you have this time?

276
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,710
I came to apologize to you.

277
00:16:44,100 --> 00:16:46,610
I didn't find out the reason...

278
00:16:47,050 --> 00:16:48,380
and misunderstood you.

279
00:16:48,940 --> 00:16:50,000
I'm at wrong.

280
00:16:50,570 --> 00:16:52,420
Please be generous...

281
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:54,090
and forgive my rudeness.

282
00:16:56,070 --> 00:16:56,950
Forget it.

283
00:16:57,130 --> 00:16:59,590
I also misunderstood
that you copied Feng Lai Yi's work.

284
00:16:59,590 --> 00:17:01,320
I guess this is my retribution.

285
00:17:08,170 --> 00:17:09,180
This...

286
00:17:09,359 --> 00:17:11,220
Why are you looking at me?
Take it.

287
00:17:11,300 --> 00:17:12,530
I've promised...

288
00:17:12,750 --> 00:17:13,720
to compensate you.

289
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:15,260
I can't break my promise.

290
00:17:15,390 --> 00:17:18,339
But I took some time to collect these.

291
00:17:20,270 --> 00:17:21,810
Just now, you said...

292
00:17:21,990 --> 00:17:23,040
we're even now.

293
00:17:23,220 --> 00:17:24,190
So,

294
00:17:24,540 --> 00:17:25,859
I can't accept this.

295
00:17:33,470 --> 00:17:35,060
The brush is made with bamboo
from Nanshan...

296
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:36,020
and fur from sheep in Zhejiang.

297
00:17:36,020 --> 00:17:37,210
Fur of old rabbit on the stone.

298
00:17:37,210 --> 00:17:38,710
The ink is from Huizhou.

299
00:17:38,930 --> 00:17:40,380
The paper is from Xuancheng.

300
00:17:40,380 --> 00:17:42,110
The inkstone is from Duanzhou.

301
00:17:42,140 --> 00:17:43,240
It's all hard to get it.

302
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,120
That's why...

303
00:17:45,040 --> 00:17:46,060
it took some time.

304
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:54,800
You really don't want it?

305
00:17:57,630 --> 00:17:58,600
Forget it then.

306
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:01,210
I can't use it anyway,
I'll just throw it away.

307
00:18:01,810 --> 00:18:03,610
These are precious things.

308
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,030
You can't throw it away.

309
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:07,040
Alright, you keep it.

310
00:18:07,530 --> 00:18:09,990
I know that giving you valuable things
is an insult to you.

311
00:18:09,990 --> 00:18:11,270
Brush, ink, paper and inkstone
are more suitable.

312
00:18:11,270 --> 00:18:13,160
We're really even now.

313
00:18:18,530 --> 00:18:19,670
Little Marquis!

314
00:18:46,120 --> 00:18:47,000
My lady.

315
00:18:47,220 --> 00:18:49,460
Is this set of stationeries expensive?

316
00:18:49,810 --> 00:18:52,070
You've been looking at it for a long time.

317
00:18:52,980 --> 00:18:53,860
It's nothing.

318
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:56,890
Have you packed the things?

319
00:18:56,980 --> 00:18:58,960
We'll go to Yun Luo Temple tomorrow.

320
00:18:58,960 --> 00:19:00,060
That fast?

321
00:19:03,230 --> 00:19:05,260
I want to meditate for a while.

322
00:19:05,610 --> 00:19:07,680
Alright, I'll go pack things now.

323
00:19:11,590 --> 00:19:15,380
[Ju Shui Pavilion]

324
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:19,120
This secret letter was exchanged
from Ruyi Pavilion...

325
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:22,050
with the two of Huang Ze's
Twelve Folding Fans of Shu.

326
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:30,560
When my mother
was meditating at Hong Fu Temple,

327
00:19:30,560 --> 00:19:32,360
Duke Su was there too.

328
00:19:33,280 --> 00:19:36,810
Eunuch Wang who serve my brother
also went there once in a hurry.

329
00:19:36,980 --> 00:19:38,260
But after the fire,

330
00:19:38,390 --> 00:19:40,120
Xu Jin came back to the capital.

331
00:19:40,190 --> 00:19:41,200
In just a few days,

332
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:43,490
he was sent to the border.

333
00:19:46,090 --> 00:19:49,040
How could there be such a coincidence?

334
00:19:51,370 --> 00:19:52,370
I'm incompetent.

335
00:19:52,780 --> 00:19:53,780
Ruyi Pavilion...

336
00:19:54,050 --> 00:19:55,910
refused to provide more secrets.

337
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:57,040
They said...

338
00:19:57,350 --> 00:19:59,730
they will only continue to cooperate...

339
00:20:00,040 --> 00:20:02,040
if we give something more valuable.

340
00:20:02,150 --> 00:20:03,030
It's enough.

341
00:20:04,660 --> 00:20:07,340
My brother must have known that
Xu Jin overturned the candlestick...

342
00:20:07,340 --> 00:20:09,320
and caused the fire in Hong Fu Temple.

343
00:20:09,320 --> 00:20:12,880
But in order to cover the truth,
he sent Xu Jin away in a hurry.

344
00:20:13,320 --> 00:20:14,200
If so,

345
00:20:14,820 --> 00:20:16,270
who should we find now?

346
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:21,420
Of course is the person who knew
about the incident.

347
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:22,300
Yes.

348
00:20:47,910 --> 00:20:48,790
What's wrong?

349
00:20:49,230 --> 00:20:50,810
This is hard for you?

350
00:20:57,630 --> 00:20:58,690
By the way,

351
00:20:58,780 --> 00:21:01,500
your birthday is in a few days.

352
00:21:02,250 --> 00:21:03,400
What do you want?

353
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,150
Ten years ago,

354
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:11,290
I thought if I solved the chess puzzle,

355
00:21:11,580 --> 00:21:12,910
my mother would return.

356
00:21:14,790 --> 00:21:16,120
I didn't expect that...

357
00:21:16,420 --> 00:21:18,280
after I solved the chess problem,

358
00:21:18,970 --> 00:21:21,130
I would be told of my mother's death.

359
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:25,130
I thought what's wrong.

360
00:21:26,940 --> 00:21:29,840
I don't want to mention
about Queen Dowager Wen...

361
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:32,300
because I'm afraid
you'll mourn the past...

362
00:21:32,300 --> 00:21:34,110
-and overthink it.
-Forget it.

363
00:21:34,900 --> 00:21:37,630
It has long past, just let it be.

364
00:21:38,420 --> 00:21:39,830
Back then,

365
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:42,820
my mother was hurriedly buried
outside of Jichang City.

366
00:21:42,820 --> 00:21:45,720
I didn't get to see her for one last time.

367
00:21:47,260 --> 00:21:48,660
Whenever I think of this,

368
00:21:49,330 --> 00:21:50,480
I feel guilty.

369
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:53,880
Rumours are spreading
like wildfire back then.

370
00:21:53,950 --> 00:21:54,950
The officials...

371
00:21:56,150 --> 00:21:58,880
disagreed to bury her
in the imperial mausoleum.

372
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:01,520
Furthermore,
she had left the palace earlier.

373
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:02,980
Her identity was awkward.

374
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:06,480
Therefore she was buried
outside of Jichang City.

375
00:22:08,300 --> 00:22:09,620
I remember that...

376
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:14,100
Eunuch Wang was not in the palace
for a while back then.

377
00:22:14,540 --> 00:22:16,570
Did you go out to hold the funeral

378
00:22:16,920 --> 00:22:18,550
for my mother?

379
00:22:22,510 --> 00:22:23,560
Yes.

380
00:22:24,050 --> 00:22:26,780
His Majesty took pity that
Queen Dowager Wen died unexpectedly

381
00:22:26,780 --> 00:22:28,800
and couldn't be buried
in the royal cemetery,

382
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:31,180
so His Majesty
ordered me to oversee the funeral.

383
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:33,020
The funeral had to be done well.

384
00:22:35,360 --> 00:22:36,890
Thanks for all these years,

385
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:39,100
brother.

386
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:41,560
Don't mention it.

387
00:22:44,680 --> 00:22:47,150
Everyone in the palace

388
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:49,300
avoided us back then.

389
00:22:50,320 --> 00:22:52,340
Only you took care of us.

390
00:22:53,040 --> 00:22:54,280
And because of this,

391
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:58,370
I never asked if you,
like the others,

392
00:22:58,460 --> 00:23:01,670
also thought that my mother's eyes
of different colour are ominous.

393
00:23:01,670 --> 00:23:03,400
What eyes of different colour?

394
00:23:03,650 --> 00:23:05,360
I dislike hearing about this.

395
00:23:09,460 --> 00:23:10,560
Back then,

396
00:23:11,260 --> 00:23:13,860
Queen Dowager Wen
took good care of me.

397
00:23:14,600 --> 00:23:18,480
That's why I love you so much.

398
00:23:21,290 --> 00:23:22,960
It has long passed.

399
00:23:24,060 --> 00:23:25,390
Don't mention it again.

400
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:44,880
Of course I know you don't believe these.

401
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:49,580
Your son, Duke Su,

402
00:23:50,510 --> 00:23:54,780
was also said to be
a bane of other's existence.

403
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:58,620
But you still entrust him
with important tasks.

404
00:24:00,190 --> 00:24:02,170
So what if you help me?

405
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:05,070
So what if you take care of me?

406
00:24:06,610 --> 00:24:09,250
To cover up your son's mistake,

407
00:24:10,570 --> 00:24:14,660
you abandon me like a shoe.

408
00:24:22,100 --> 00:24:25,400
[Ruyi Pavilion]

409
00:24:27,070 --> 00:24:29,270
Is Ms Fu Rong here?

410
00:24:30,860 --> 00:24:32,310
She just went out.

411
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:33,450
Who are you?

412
00:24:34,070 --> 00:24:35,480
Princess Consort of Qingping
invites Ms Fu Rong

413
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:38,380
[Su Yu, palace servant]

414
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:36,750
to attend her conferment banquet.

415
00:24:36,840 --> 00:24:38,340
Please give this to her.

416
00:24:38,470 --> 00:24:39,830
[Invitation]

417
00:24:40,930 --> 00:24:41,810
Alright.

418
00:24:44,320 --> 00:24:46,340
You're in a good mood
these few days.

419
00:24:47,840 --> 00:24:49,250
Master is safe

420
00:24:49,420 --> 00:24:52,080
and sister has arrived
at Yun Luo Temple safely.

421
00:24:55,280 --> 00:24:56,950
[Invitation]

422
00:24:57,560 --> 00:25:00,090
Zhu'er invited me
to her conferment banquet.

423
00:25:01,660 --> 00:25:02,710
Maybe

424
00:25:03,460 --> 00:25:05,460
we can go back to the way things were.

425
00:25:08,390 --> 00:25:10,500
Hurry up and make more delicacies.

426
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:12,560
It's all her favourites.

427
00:25:13,450 --> 00:25:14,460
Young Lady Fu Rong.

428
00:25:14,460 --> 00:25:17,060
Don't forget Ms Qi's favourite.

429
00:25:17,360 --> 00:25:18,420
Yes.

430
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:19,520
That's the one.

431
00:25:20,050 --> 00:25:21,450
Zhu'er loves to eat this.

432
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:24,120
We went to get dates together
when we were young.

433
00:25:24,140 --> 00:25:27,000
Ms Qi will be very happy
when she receives this gift.

434
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:39,850
I need to make her
a new piece of jewellery.

435
00:25:40,770 --> 00:25:43,630
[Dong Residence]

436
00:26:08,050 --> 00:26:09,110
Mr Dong.

437
00:26:14,120 --> 00:26:15,000
Who are you?

438
00:26:16,020 --> 00:26:17,150
That folding fan...

439
00:26:20,370 --> 00:26:23,760
When Huang Ze passed through Shu,

440
00:26:24,550 --> 00:26:26,480
he saw the beautiful scenery of Shu

441
00:26:27,100 --> 00:26:29,300
and settled down in Shu.

442
00:26:30,320 --> 00:26:32,650
He left twelve folding fans.

443
00:26:34,940 --> 00:26:36,430
Each of his folding fans

444
00:26:38,630 --> 00:26:40,920
is breath-taking.

445
00:26:41,670 --> 00:26:44,800
Not to mention when twelve fans
are connected together,

446
00:26:45,190 --> 00:26:48,050
it's a beautiful map of Shu.

447
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:51,050
Twenty-five years ago,

448
00:26:51,170 --> 00:26:52,670
a new magistrate
was appointed in Yizhou.

449
00:26:52,670 --> 00:26:53,770
He liked Huang Ze.

450
00:26:54,690 --> 00:26:57,640
He was fortunate enough to see the elegance
of these twelve holding fans.

451
00:26:57,640 --> 00:26:59,640
He offered a lot of money to buy them.

452
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:03,270
However, the descendants of the
Huang Family were unwilling to sell it.

453
00:27:03,270 --> 00:27:04,150
Enough!

454
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:07,360
Mr Dong.

455
00:27:08,020 --> 00:27:09,920
Do you still remember
the treachery incident

456
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:11,760
in Yizhou 25 years ago?

457
00:27:12,820 --> 00:27:15,330
It's just some scholars
who wrote a few novels...

458
00:27:15,330 --> 00:27:16,820
to make a living.

459
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:19,440
Someone tampered with the contents

460
00:27:19,900 --> 00:27:21,660
and they were convicted of treason.

461
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:24,130
Everyone involved in the case
was beheaded in public.

462
00:27:24,130 --> 00:27:26,460
All property were confiscated.

463
00:27:27,300 --> 00:27:29,140
I didn't accept those holding fans.

464
00:27:29,140 --> 00:27:31,260
What has it got to do with me?

465
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:35,480
You didn't kill them

466
00:27:35,830 --> 00:27:37,900
but you caused their deaths.

467
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:41,090
In these 25 years,

468
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:43,440
these 12 folding fans were separated.

469
00:27:44,590 --> 00:27:48,680
In the end, ten of the folding fans
fell into the hand of Wu You, the profiteer.

470
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:51,140
Wu You is not a good man.

471
00:27:51,230 --> 00:27:52,630
He did many wrongdoings.

472
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:54,490
In order to see him,

473
00:27:54,930 --> 00:27:56,660
I went through a lot of trouble.

474
00:27:56,950 --> 00:27:58,480
[In the spring and summer,]

475
00:27:58,840 --> 00:28:00,120
[flowers bloom.]

476
00:28:00,780 --> 00:28:02,140
[The theme is flower.]

477
00:28:02,410 --> 00:28:04,390
[Peony is the king of flowers.]

478
00:28:04,740 --> 00:28:06,340
[It implies good meanings.]

479
00:28:07,250 --> 00:28:09,180
[Thank you for the suggestion.]

480
00:28:10,500 --> 00:28:11,780
[Ruyi Pavilion]

481
00:28:12,090 --> 00:28:15,210
[will make peony head ornament
for Consort Shu.]

482
00:28:15,830 --> 00:28:18,290
[When I was thinking about
how to get close to Wu You,]

483
00:28:18,290 --> 00:28:20,220
[someone gave me an opportunity.]

484
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:21,720
[Beauty!]

485
00:28:22,030 --> 00:28:23,480
[Beauty, don't go!]

486
00:28:24,500 --> 00:28:26,040
[Beauty, don't go.]

487
00:28:26,960 --> 00:28:28,020
[Don't be shy.]

488
00:28:28,190 --> 00:28:30,120
[We're a family since we're here.]

489
00:28:30,700 --> 00:28:31,580
[I'm Wu You.]

490
00:28:31,710 --> 00:28:33,600
[Just call me Brother You.]

491
00:28:34,130 --> 00:28:35,790
[Wu You, don't make trouble!]

492
00:28:40,950 --> 00:28:42,100
Who are you?

493
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:44,040
How do you know about this?

494
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:52,830
Because I'm the owner of Ruyi Pavilion.

495
00:28:54,420 --> 00:28:55,380
Impossible.

496
00:28:56,530 --> 00:28:57,760
You're just...

497
00:29:00,090 --> 00:29:01,630
Not that jewellery store,

498
00:29:02,950 --> 00:29:04,050
but

499
00:29:05,770 --> 00:29:07,530
the legendary Ruyi Pavilion.

500
00:29:10,260 --> 00:29:12,100
Since you know it,

501
00:29:12,410 --> 00:29:13,910
this is great.

502
00:29:15,490 --> 00:29:18,130
I just need you to do me a small favour.

503
00:29:19,190 --> 00:29:20,330
When it's done,

504
00:29:20,900 --> 00:29:23,940
those past events
will be like these folding fans.

505
00:29:24,030 --> 00:29:26,670
Whether you want to keep it
or destroy it,

506
00:29:26,840 --> 00:29:28,120
it's up to you.

507
00:29:28,650 --> 00:29:29,840
After that,

508
00:29:30,190 --> 00:29:32,120
you can rest assured.

509
00:29:34,410 --> 00:29:37,140
For you to collect all 12 folding fans,

510
00:29:37,270 --> 00:29:39,960
I specially bought these two folding fans.

511
00:29:40,040 --> 00:29:42,240
Now these 12 folding fans are united.

512
00:29:42,950 --> 00:29:44,440
Mr Dong.

513
00:29:44,530 --> 00:29:46,860
Don't let me down.

514
00:29:50,300 --> 00:29:52,850
I made a mistake back then.

515
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:55,170
Since I became an official,

516
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:57,170
I'm cautious and conscientious.

517
00:29:57,560 --> 00:29:59,160
I've never taken any bribes.

518
00:29:59,450 --> 00:30:02,350
But why did you find me?

519
00:30:06,620 --> 00:30:07,720
Mr Dong.

520
00:30:07,980 --> 00:30:10,180
Everyone should bear the consequences

521
00:30:10,270 --> 00:30:11,460
of their mistakes.

522
00:30:12,210 --> 00:30:13,790
My only son is born sick.

523
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:16,610
It's still not clear
if he can live past ten years old.

524
00:30:16,610 --> 00:30:18,410
Is this punishment not enough?

525
00:30:21,840 --> 00:30:24,660
You're cautious and conscientious,
and you serve the public wholeheartedly.

526
00:30:24,660 --> 00:30:26,380
This is your duty.

527
00:30:26,900 --> 00:30:29,050
It's not enough to make up
for your mistake.

528
00:30:29,050 --> 00:30:29,930
However,

529
00:30:30,510 --> 00:30:33,370
I know you're an upright official.

530
00:30:34,080 --> 00:30:37,200
So, I don't want to
make it difficult for you.

531
00:30:42,740 --> 00:30:45,650
If you're unwilling to cooperate,

532
00:30:46,260 --> 00:30:48,110
and your crime is exposed,

533
00:30:49,260 --> 00:30:52,640
your good name will be ruined.

534
00:30:52,860 --> 00:30:56,470
Your sister and two nephews
may still have a way out.

535
00:30:58,720 --> 00:31:00,870
However,
for your weak young son,

536
00:31:01,270 --> 00:31:03,420
how can he live?

537
00:31:25,560 --> 00:31:27,760
[Qin Qing]

538
00:31:31,410 --> 00:31:33,960
[Dong Fang Li]

539
00:32:14,260 --> 00:32:15,230
Mr Dong.

540
00:32:15,500 --> 00:32:18,050
Wu You kept saying he's not feeling well
since this morning.

541
00:32:18,050 --> 00:32:20,780
I thought he was just
making up excuses to escape.

542
00:32:20,910 --> 00:32:22,050
So, I ignored him.

543
00:32:22,450 --> 00:32:24,870
But he suddenly foamed at the mouth

544
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:26,140
and died.

545
00:32:27,290 --> 00:32:29,400
[Ruyi Pavilion.]

546
00:32:30,190 --> 00:32:32,440
[You're really ruthless.]

547
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:46,780
Dong Fang Li?

548
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:50,880
That Dong Fang Li who is in charge of
the imperial storehouse?

549
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:51,800
That's right.

550
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:55,540
When I first received news
from Ruyi Pavilion,

